item.title: Episode 128 From Sleeping in Her Car to a $60 million brand - Alpha Femme- Melanie Ann Layer
item.description:
In this episode, we have a deeply moving conversation with Melanie Ann Layer. She is the Founder of the Alpha Femme online coaching brand that started in 2017. Since 2017 her company has impacted thousands of clients and generated over $60 million in sales.

Her journey started out by sleeping in her car where she witnessed a woman jump out of a window to then become committed to the journey of personal development... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/915826.rss
